import { Navbar, Nav, Container, Form, FormControl, Button
      } from 'react-bootstrap';

export const Header = () => {
  return (
    <header>
      <Navbar collapseOnSelect fixed="top" expand="md" bg="dark" variant="dark">
      <Container>
        <Navbar.Toggle />

        <Navbar.Brand href="/">The Lord of The Rings API
        </Navbar.Brand>

        <Navbar.Collapse>
          <Nav fill>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link href="#Home">Home</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link href="#Books">Books</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link href="#Chapters">Chapters</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link href="#Characters">Characters</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link href="#Movies">Movies</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
            <Nav.Item>
              <Nav.Link href="#Quotes">Quotes</Nav.Link>
            </Nav.Item>
          </Nav> 
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
      </Navbar>
    </header>
  );
}
